"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-showbiz-tv-radio-1934816-bbc-olympics-2024-paris-switch-off\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  BBCOlympicsviewers were not impressed as the channel aired Paris' closing ceremony for the 2024 event.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 104, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 61, \"end\": 66, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999953793122, \"rank\": 4.620538021004868e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"AsClare Baldingwelcomed viewers to the proceedings, fans rushed to social media to rage as the show began airing onBBCat 7pm, but the ceremony did not start until 8pm.\", \"from\": 106, \"to\": 273, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Other viewers were left fuming as Olympic champions Laura Kenny and Chris Hoy, who were helping present the event, were joined by First Dates host Fred Sirieix, whose daughter won a bronze in the synchronised women's diving for 10m.\", \"from\": 275, \"to\": 507, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 327, \"end\": 338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Kenny\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laura Kenny\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Kenny\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Kenny\"}, {\"begin\": 343, \"end\": 352, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hoy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chris Hoy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hoy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hoy\"}, {\"begin\": 405, \"end\": 416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/First_Dates\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.228546170456416e-26, \"text\": \"First Dates\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/First_Dates\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/First_Dates\"}, {\"begin\": 422, \"end\": 434, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Sirieix\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fred Sirieix\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Sirieix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Sirieix\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One viewer said: \\\"So the #ClosingCeremony starts at 8?\", \"from\": 509, \"to\": 563, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And the bloody BBC are just going to talk about it for an entire hour?\", \"from\": 564, \"to\": 634, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 579, \"end\": 582, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.5858893542818248, \"rank\": 0.6930489850420422, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yeah, no.\\\"\", \"from\": 635, \"to\": 645, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Another added: \\\"Have just switched OFF this on BBC1 #ClosingCeremony what on earth has Fred Siriex got to do with broadcasting ( yes daughter diving) The entire BBC coverage has been appalling.\", \"from\": 647, \"to\": 840, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 808, \"end\": 811, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.5858893542818248, \"rank\": 0.6930489850420422, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From dreaded know nothing but statistics Balding to scruffily dressed presenters.\\\"\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 923, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A third chipped in: \\\"BBC or Eurosport?\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 965, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 948, \"end\": 951, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.5858893542818248, \"rank\": 0.6930489850420422, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Clare Balding or Laura Woods?\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 995, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 966, \"end\": 979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clare_Balding\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Clare Balding\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clare_Balding\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clare_Balding\"}, {\"begin\": 983, \"end\": 994, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_J._Woods\", \"score\": 0.9995515489768271, \"rank\": 0.00023613245403570208, \"text\": \"Laura Woods\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_J._Woods\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_J._Woods\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hmmm\\u2026..difficult!\\\"\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1014, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A fourth wrote: \\\"Fred Siriex feels like a spare part leading up the closing ceremony.\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1101, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Love Laura Kenny & Chris Hoy though,\\\" as a fifth agreed: \\\"Why Fred Siriex is there?\", \"from\": 1102, \"to\": 1185, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1121, \"end\": 1130, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hoy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chris Hoy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hoy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hoy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Come on BBC, grow up.\\\"\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1208, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1194, \"end\": 1197, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.5858893542818248, \"rank\": 0.6930489850420422, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But one fan gushed: \\\"If you'd told me at the start of the year that one of the best additions to the BBC Olympic punditry team would be Fred from First Dates I'd have had a little chuckle, but he's lit up the screen every time he's been on, and just seems like a lovely man.\\\"\", \"from\": 1210, \"to\": 1485, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1311, \"end\": 1314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.5858893542818248, \"rank\": 0.6930489850420422, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fred has been commentating throughout the competition due to his daughter Andrea competing, and left viewers emotional as he consoled his daughter on camera in a sweet moment.\", \"from\": 1487, \"to\": 1662, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss:Team GB sends Olympics viewers into frenzy as they all point out same thing  Do not miss:BBC's Michael Johnson shuts down Piers Morgan after 'schooling' him  Do not miss:Paris Olympics 2024 final medal table as Team GB come seventh in the world  If you'd told me at the start of the year that one of the best additions to the BBC Olympic punditry team would be Fred from First Dates I'd have had a little chuckle, but he's lit up the screen every time he's been on, and just seems like a lovely man  Following her bronze win, Andrea said: \\\"Obviously it wasn't the result that I wanted, but I am not even upset at the competition, the girls dove amazing and did better than me and it wasn't meant to be.\", \"from\": 1664, \"to\": 2378, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1676, \"end\": 1683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9098982196842726, \"rank\": 0.07866615708857641, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_G